<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.6.11">
<l>kaṇṇit taṇṇan tuḻāy muṭikkamalat taṭamperuṅ kaṇṇaṉaippukaḻ</l>
<l>naṇṇi teṉkurukūrc caṭakōpaṉ māṟaṉcoṉṉa</l>
<l>veṇṇil cōrvi lntāti yāyirattu ḷivaiyu mōrpat ticaiyōṭum</l>
<l>paṇṇil pāṭa vallāravar kēcavaṉ ṟamarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those capable of singing in service</l>
<l>together with music these one ten among the thousand of countless, flawless Antāti</l>
<l>spoken by Caṭakōpaṉ Māṟaṉ of southern Kurukūr, reaching fame,</l>
<l>on Kṛṣṇa with broad big lotus eyes [and] a crown of cool Tulsi in a chaplet</l>
	<l>will be Keśava’s people.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
